    "body": "Correct. chicken and egg problem with the state and block roots again.\r\n\r\nI see two solutions:\r\n* Locally use `b'\\x00'*32` as a synonym to the genesis block root wrt to finality (don't revert past 0x00 means do revert past genesis block)\r\n* We can \"surgically\" add in previous and current justified_root as well as finalized_root in `cache_state` on the first transition after the genesis_slot. This would require putting a little bit of exceptional logic into the validator guide to explicitly handle attesting to his case.",
